rComments: Fantastic. Subbed in SOC101, didn't get to develop own curriculum, still added. This course is awesome: no text, free download papers, project is soc. observations, not just an essay. Includes lots of her current observations/pictures to add to lectures. So funny too! Very approachable, tries to get to know you. Hope for more courses with her!
Totally awesome prof. knows a lot but is pretty funny so  her lectures are easy to follow. Some of my friends even came to hear her.
Prof Kenny is the best prof EVER. She's funny and engaging and incredibly smart. I learned a lot in this class.
Kenny is a great, animated professor. It's unfortunate she has to read Brym's notes, with her own stuff she is easy to follow and well liked. She is funny and at the same time able to keep focus.
She reads, literally, READS from a paper at lecture. Enough said.

I absolutely loved this class and cannot say enough about Prof Kenny. The material was challenging at times but the lectures and assignments were creative and interesting. She really just wants you to learn, do well and take something away from the course. She's very witty and down to earth. Awesome!
